tes inc  elm street new canaan ct ph    fx    marketingarmstrongshawcom   wwwarmstrongshawcomyour use of this site signifies that you accept our terms of useprivacy policy armstrong shaw  product armstrong shaw has a disciplined absolute value approach to the equity market  we believe that investing in high quality businesses run by proven management teams at attractive prices will provide superior returns to our clients over time  we seek to provide attractive long term returns by investing in a concentrated portfolio assembled through bottom up fundamentally driven stock selection  we invest in securities when cash flow or asset value analysis determines they are selling at a substantial discount to intrinsic value  we focus on companies that generate predictable and sustainable free cash flows  high cash flow generation allows for increased research and development the ability to capitalize quickly on opportunities make acquisitions to further grow the business or return value to shareholders  we also compare the companys valutation to its peers the broader market and any transactions that may have taken place in its industry  we interview the management team to get a better sense of the strategic and financial plans for the company  ultimately our goal is to purchase these stocks at prices equal to or less than  of our estimate of intrinsic valuehomeproductinvestment teamcontactterms of usecompany specific analysis  what we look forarmstrong shaw associates inc  elm street new canaan ct ph    fx    marketingarmstrongshawcom   wwwarmstrongshawcomyour use of this site signifies that you accept our terms of useprivacy policyour product armstrong shaw associates inc ct takes position in pentair plc nysepnr  daily political home aboutcontact columnists privacy policy headlines politics nation world issues economy finance pentair plc  get news  ratings daily enter your email address below to get the latest news and analysts ratings for pentair plc with our free daily 